SECURITY DISCLAIMER

This software is designed for monitoring driver loads on Windows systems and
is NOT suitable for production security monitoring. It has limitations and may
not detect all driver loading methods, especially sophisticated rootkits or
kernel-level malware.

The software requires Administrator privileges to function and should be used
with caution and understanding of the security implications.

